Stills</PERSON> soon thereafter; he teamed with Stills in <LOCATION>Buffalo
Springfield</LOCATION> and <PERSON>Crosby</PERSON>, <ORGANIZATION>Stills Nash &amp; Young</ORGANIZATION>.
