Lynn Anne Hanson of Monrovia contra-dances in Anaheim with Allen Paulson, who 
kicks up heels when away from Oregon home. ; Photo, Contra dancers in Anaheim 
include all ages and choice of clothes, including Sabin Stewart, 12, of Garden 
Grove, leading his group in a circle. ADRIENNE HELITZER / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Zona Gray-Blair of Brea gets her son, David, 15 months, started dancing 
early, to delight of their partners. ; Photo, Wayne Battleson of Garden Grove 
calls 12 to 15 dances a night, each 10 minutes long. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
