<P>
Photo, Leo Kottke, in Ventura Tuesday, will play tonight in Anaheim: "It took 
me a while to realize who I was vocally. I can't just open my mouth and 
holler." MICHAEL BAKER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
