Club</ORGANIZATION>, 634 <ORGANIZATION>State St.</ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION>Santa Barbara</LOCATION>. For information, call, 963-9991. Tickets 
are <MONEY>$5</MONEY>. 
</P></TEXT>
