the opening spot Monday at the Crazy Horse Steak House in Santa Ana. ; Photo, 
Asleep at the Wheel's Ray Benson, frontman, guitarist and singer, clowns during 
last number. KARI RENE HALL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
